result.name: Typhoon

reviews.text: Interesting bar in Wan Chai with very different vibes. On Wednesday, the place is a vibrant dance club playing top 40s bursting out the door. On a Saturday night, they're calmly playing American Country music with motocross on the TV. Very intriguing place, but the drink prices are fantastic.

Worst bar ever....  there was a female that was either plastered or crazy and she was going around making a horrible scene. She hit another person that she DIDN’T know so hard on the head to a point we were concerned she suffered a concussion. She was ready to fight someone for no apparent reason. Everybody witnessed it, including the bouncers and the bartenders. The bouncers did not do anything and the person who was hit had to leave instead :( why aren’t they doing their job?
One of the best places for watching football in Wanchai with friends, always a good crowd
They sure know how to pull a Gunniess. Good vibes and good service.
Nice place with good crowd.
